\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces TmFeO$_3$ crystal structure with Fe–Tm chi coupling bonds. Circles: Fe sublattices (red/purple/teal/orange = sub 0/1/2/3). Squares: Tm sublattices (blues/greys/yellow). Solid lines: even bonds (sign$_{57}=+1$); dashed: odd bonds (sign$_{57}=-1$). Colours: orbit 1 (red), 2 (blue), 3 (green), 4 (orange). Each Tm sublattice has exactly one bond per orbit, connecting it to all four Fe sublattices.}}{4}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
